response.original_title: Time Management from the Inside Out
response.overview: Building upon the success of her bestselling book and PBS pledge success "Organizing from the Inside Out," Julie Morgenstern offers an entirely new, breakthrough system for taking control of your schedule and your life. In this program, Julie offers invaluable new insights and tools that will help viewers take control of their time, and help each of us have the time for what's really important in our lives.
response.title: Time Management from the Inside Out
